♪I've said goodbye a thousand times♪

192
00:14:22,240 --> 00:14:26,180
♪Only to call your name again♪

193
00:14:26,520 --> 00:14:29,890
♪For it's the only thing♪

194
00:14:30,390 --> 00:14:34,190
♪I'll never forget♪

195
00:14:38,060 --> 00:14:41,430
♪Till the day that I die♪
